name: The magic of mushrooms
description: Psilocybe cubensis is a species of psychedelic mushroom whose principal active compounds are psilocybin and psilocin. The mind-altering effects of psilocybin-containing mushrooms typically last from three to eight hours depending on dosage, preparation method, and personal metabolism. The first 3–4 hours after ingestion are typically referred to as the 'peak' in which the user experiences more vivid visuals and distortions in reality.
